itlr"},"question_content":"WEB初级工程师（CSS，暂时不考虑JS）指的是能独立完成项目。 至少应该具备以下的能力： 1.能够独立的完成项目，完美还原设计稿. 2.能够支持自适应，不能做自适应的网站已经很少了. 3.能够支持响应式，毕竟跨屏的场景越来越多了. 4.能够了解一门CSS框架，做为提炼自已抽象能力的引子，通过使用，来直观的感受到其他人是怎么解决代码复用问题的。 5.能够和其他的项目组成员沟通学习交流协作，熟悉一些编码规范. 然后，并不要求这个…","topices":[{"title":"HTML","url":"//www.zhihu.com/topic/19551323"},{"title":"CSS","url":"//www.zhihu.com/topic/19551326"},{"title":"JavaScript","url":"//www.zhihu.com/topic/19552521"},{"title":"HTML5","url":"//www.zhihu.com/topic/19557564"},{"title":"CSS3","url":"//www.zhihu.com/topic/19562598"}],"attention_count":"1223","view_count":"80483","answers":[{"answer_ID":"69156567","url":"http://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/69156567","content":"<b>前言</b> <b>===============================</b> <b> CSS入门比较简单，很适合零基础的人去学习。</b> <b>但是该从哪里开始呢？又该学到什么程度，学会了之后，又会能找到一份什么样的工作呢。</b> <b>首页，我必须要告诉你们，IT修真院的弟子们是可以在一个月之内胜任初级CSS工程师的…</b>","createdTime":1445669900,"author":{"avatarUrlTemplate":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0fddeeca2cc0f98b1adbb39f0440f56c_{size}.jpg","type":"people","name":"暗灭","url":"http://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/579c732d98e3797028793bb456af7b2b","gender":1,"userType":"people","urlToken":"ptteng","isAdvertiser":false,"avatarUrl":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0fddeeca2cc0f98b1adbb39f0440f56c_is.jpg","isOrg":false,"headline":"京华九月秋近寒，浮沉半生影长单","followerCount":20485,"badge":[],"id":"579c732d98e3797028793bb456af7b2b"},"updatedTime":1508852545},{"answer_ID":"70156170","url":"http://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/70156170","content":"实际项目写CSS是这样的，有个idea，但不知道或者忘了具体CSS该怎么写，于是Google一下，找到一些东西，比如常见的CSS Tricks网站上有很多整理好现成的代码可用，然后在Devtools里面试一试效果，能解决大部分的CSS编程问题。所以其实并不需要一个月，网上搜…","createdTime":1446260211,"author":{"avatarUrlTemplate":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/7ba7ab10a562016b6ec063a6d43c1587_{size}.jpg","type":"people","name":"itlr","url":"http://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/72d26f9f0c7c6d0b2bab73418c595c6b","gender":1,"userType":"people","urlToken":"itlr","isAdvertiser":false,"avatarUrl":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/7ba7ab10a562016b6ec063a6d43c1587_is.jpg","i